name: ROOK II - WHITE
description:
High Quality Jiu-Jitsu Kimono. Jiu-Jitsu is often compared to Chess. The strategy, careful movement, the need to think moves ahead of your opponent, the checkmate(submission) are all things that make Jiu-Jitsu comparable. Jiu-Jitsu is a thinking man's game, and so is Chess. This was our inspiration behind this gi. 


-450gr Lightweight One Piece High Tech Weave top.
-Ripstop Pants
-Ripstop collar w/ EVA foam inside. Both to prevent harboring of bacteria, and to allow quick drying.
-Embroidered logos.
-Black Trim/Dark Grey Stitching

-Comes with Ripstop carrying bag

name: KIDS-LITTLE SUPREME
description:
SUPREME STANDARD KIDS KIMONO

This is our traditional styling gi. Simple & Clean Design. It's lightweight makes it very comfortable for kids. If you like minimalist styling, you'll like this gi. 

** NOTE: Size M0 has elastic waistband to help small kids keep pants on while training. We've found the smallest kids often need their pants tied and have to stop training to re-tie. Elastic waist prevents this distraction. Size M1 to Size P have Rope Drawstring.   

-Super Light 350gr One Piece Lightweight Pearl Weave top. 
-Lightweight Twill Pants 
-EVA foam inside Collar to prevent harboring of bacteria, and to allow quick drying. 
-Blue Embroidered logos 
-Blue Trim 
-Light Grey Stitching
-Top Quality Construction
-Includes Ripstop Cotton Tote Bag.
